# ERD (Text Version)

## Entities

### User
- id (PK)
- username
- email
- password
- created_at

### Post
- id (PK)
- user_id (FK -> User.id)
- title
- content
- created_at

### Comment
- id (PK)
- post_id (FK -> Post.id)
- user_id (FK -> User.id)
- content
- created_at

### Vote
- id (PK)
- post_id (FK -> Post.id)
- user_id (FK -> User.id)
- type (UP/DOWN)

## Relationships
- User 1:N Post
- User 1:N Comment
- User 1:N Vote
- Post 1:N Comment
- Post 1:N Vote


# API Specification

## Auth
### POST /auth/register
- Request: username, email, password
- Response: user info

### POST /auth/login
- Request: email, password
- Response: JWT token

## Users
### GET /users/{id}
- Response: user profile

## Posts
### GET /posts
- Query: page, size
- Response: list of posts

### POST /posts
- Auth required
- Body: title, content

### GET /posts/{id}
- Response: post detail

### DELETE /posts/{id}
- Auth required

## Comments
### POST /posts/{id}/comments
- Body: content

### DELETE /comments/{id}

## Votes
### POST /posts/{id}/vote
- Body: type (UP/DOWN)
